<div  class='hr av-dzta7c-1fbae04974345a523e17f2dc34b696a2 hr-default  avia-builder-el-13  el_after_av_one_fourth  el_before_av_textblock '><span class='hr-inner '><span class="hr-inner-style"></span></span></div>
<section  class='av_textblock_section av-c5sb7s-a529b27a3f23f55859a3894975a45acb'  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock'  itemprop="text" ><h1>Museums in Cape Town</h1>
<p>The Cape Town Diamond Museum is definitely one of the museums in Cape Town that you simply have to visit. It is a little hidden gem!</p>
<p>Experience diamonds like never before. Learn about the diamond industry, the <a href="https://www.capetowndiamondmuseum.org/about-diamonds/south-african-diamond-history/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>history of diamonds</strong></a> and diamonds in South Africa. You can expect an intimate tour and learning experience when <a href="https://www.capetowndiamondmuseum.org/visiting/visiting-information/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>visiting</strong></a> the diamond museum. Expect to see mining gear, famous diamond replicas, historical artefacts, specimens of natural kimberlite and much more. You will also have the chance to see how diamond jewellery is manufactured to the final product.</p>
<p>The museum is a non-profit organisation focused on creating a new appreciation for diamonds and the diamond industry. It is a gift from Shimansky to the public. Be sure to pop in for a tour when you are visiting the museums at the V&amp;A Waterfront in Cape Town. <strong><a href="https://www.capetowndiamondmuseum.org/contact/diamond-tour-booking-form/">Book in advance</a></strong> to avoid disappointment.<br />
Experience, discover, explore and learn at the Cape Town Diamond Museum.<br />
